<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>119</hymn_number>
<key>Ab</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 A kan Khamhbawi a lu cungah, A lianhngannak a hmun; A sunparnak a cer
 a tlang, A hmur in vel a luang, A hmur in vel a luang.

[V2]
 Jesuh Khrih he tahchunh awk tlak, Ahohmanh an um lo; Vancungmi hna lak
 hmanh ah khin, A lomi an um lo, A lomi an um lo.

[V3]
 Sifahnak nih a ka phum kha, Jesuh nih a ka hmuh, Ningzah tih awk
 vailam put in, Ka ngaihchiatnak a phorh, Ka ngaihchiatnak a phorh.

[V4]
 Jesuh zohkhenh domhtlaihnak in, Keimah ka lu a nung, Thihnak kha ka
 tei khawh naklai, (Thlan in a ka khamh cang)2

[V5]
 Amah umnak vancung khua ah, Keimah a ka kalpi, Ka Pa lianhnak a ka
 hmuhter, (Ka lunglawmhnak a tling)2

[V6]
 Pathian a ngan velngeihnak kha, Keimah ka hmuh dah ngai, Ka lung
 thonghra ngei hmanhning law, (Bawipa ka chanh dih lai)2.</lyrics>
<title>SUNPARNAK A UM CH119</title>
</song>